{
  "video_id": "kvdHqS3ryw0",
  "title": "How to get serious about diversity and inclusion in the workplace | Janet Stovall",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13507.0,
      "end_time": 16777.0,
      "text": "Everybody has that one friend --"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16801.0,
      "end_time": 18625.0,
      "text": "you know, the single-minded one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18649.0,
      "end_time": 21824.0,
      "text": "the one who, no matter what the question is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21848.0,
      "end_time": 26120.0,
      "text": "always finds a way to make the answer whatever it is she&#39;s single-minded about."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26769.0,
      "end_time": 27982.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m that friend."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28600.0,
      "end_time": 29779.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29803.0,
      "end_time": 32386.0,
      "text": "And the thing that I&#39;m single-minded about"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32409.0,
      "end_time": 33592.0,
      "text": "is racism."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34100.0,
      "end_time": 38436.0,
      "text": "If someone were to ask me, \"So, Janet, got any plans for the 4th of July?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38460.0,
      "end_time": 41529.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m subject to answer, \"Yeah, I&#39;m going to binge-watch &#39;Roots.&#39;\""
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41553.0,
      "end_time": 42608.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42633.0,
      "end_time": 45509.0,
      "text": "Or if they said, \"Janet, I&#39;ve got a joke for you:"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45533.0,
      "end_time": 47382.0,
      "text": "Why&#39;d the chicken cross the road?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47406.0,
      "end_time": 49567.0,
      "text": "\"Uh, was it a black chicken?"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49591.0,
      "end_time": 51204.0,
      "text": "Probably gentrification.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51228.0,
      "end_time": 53428.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54657.0,
      "end_time": 57553.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61650.0,
      "end_time": 65628.0,
      "text": "But for me, single-mindedness is not just caring about something."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65653.0,
      "end_time": 69414.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s caring about something enough to do something about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 69903.0,
      "end_time": 73810.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not just thinking, it&#39;s doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 73520.0,
      "end_time": 77363.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not just praying, it is moving your feet."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 78292.0,
      "end_time": 82970.0,
      "text": "And the reason I&#39;m single-minded about racism is because I know"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82994.0,
      "end_time": 86790.0,
      "text": "single-mindedness can destroy it."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 86103.0,
      "end_time": 88250.0,
      "text": "I learned that many, many years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 88274.0,
      "end_time": 91968.0,
      "text": "Back in 1984, I was a junior at Davidson College"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 91992.0,
      "end_time": 93607.0,
      "text": "in Davidson, North Carolina."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 94126.0,
      "end_time": 96513.0,
      "text": "Now, Davidson is a little-bitty town,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 96537.0,
      "end_time": 98933.0,
      "text": "Southern town, split by railroad tracks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 98957.0,
      "end_time": 102722.0,
      "text": "with white Davidson on one side, black Davidson on the other side,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 102746.0,
      "end_time": 106470.0,
      "text": "and, as black students lived on the white side of the tracks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 106710.0,
      "end_time": 109561.0,
      "text": "we got used to being stopped in downtown and asked for ID,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 110259.0,
      "end_time": 113353.0,
      "text": "until the police memorized our faces."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 113377.0,
      "end_time": 115452.0,
      "text": "But fortunately, that didn&#39;t take too long,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 115476.0,
      "end_time": 119132.0,
      "text": "because out of 1,200 students, only 52 of us were black."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 119156.0,
      "end_time": 120963.0,
      "text": "There was on black professor"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 120987.0,
      "end_time": 122663.0,
      "text": "and one black assistant dean."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 123194.0,
      "end_time": 125720.0,
      "text": "Things weren&#39;t a lot better on campus."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 125657.0,
      "end_time": 127954.0,
      "text": "Well, I wasn&#39;t OK with this."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 128359.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130507.00000000001,
      "text": "And so, I started writing things."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 130531.0,
      "end_time": 132516.0,
      "text": "And then I started yelling things."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 132540.0,
      "end_time": 134292.0,
      "text": "And after about three years of that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 134317.0,
      "end_time": 135600.0,
      "text": "I got tired."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 135624.0,
      "end_time": 138507.0,
      "text": "So I decided to write one more thing;"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 138532.0,
      "end_time": 141970.0,
      "text": "I wrote something called \"Project &#39;87.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 141788.0,
      "end_time": 145368.0,
      "text": "Project &#39;87 was really just a challenge to Davidson:"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 145953.0,
      "end_time": 148636.0,
      "text": "in three years, by 1987,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 148660.0,
      "end_time": 150771.0,
      "text": "enroll 100 black students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 151387.0,
      "end_time": 153581.0,
      "text": "hire 10 black professors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 154589.0,
      "end_time": 156859.0,
      "text": "create five Black Studies classes"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 156883.0,
      "end_time": 158687.0,
      "text": "and hire one black dean."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 159330.0,
      "end_time": 161616.0,
      "text": "It didn&#39;t seem particularly revolutionary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 161640.0,
      "end_time": 163738.0,
      "text": "but what was different about it was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 163763.0,
      "end_time": 167541.0,
      "text": "we also challenged Davidson to say that if you don&#39;t do this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 167565.0,
      "end_time": 170470.0,
      "text": "we will question your commitment to diversity."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 170946.0,
      "end_time": 172399.0,
      "text": "It was a real problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 172423.0,
      "end_time": 174234.0,
      "text": "We put some real numbers to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 174258.0,
      "end_time": 176479.0,
      "text": "We gave them some real consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 176503.0,
      "end_time": 178773.0,
      "text": "Well, the campus went absolutely nuts."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 179316.0,
      "end_time": 181962.0,
      "text": "But fortunately, in the middle of this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 181986.0,
      "end_time": 183911.0,
      "text": "Davidson got a new president,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 183936.0,
      "end_time": 187590.0,
      "text": "and that president was single-minded about racism, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 187632.0,
      "end_time": 189776.0,
      "text": "And so, he created a task force"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 190490.0,
      "end_time": 192948.0,
      "text": "to address the issues in Project &#39;87."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 192972.0,
      "end_time": 194907.0,
      "text": "And several months after that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 194931.0,
      "end_time": 198427.0,
      "text": "we produced a 77-page report."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 199244.0,
      "end_time": 204149.0,
      "text": "That report was the foundation for all the change that came after it."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 204882.0,
      "end_time": 207684.0,
      "text": "Now, I wasn&#39;t there to see that change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 207708.0,
      "end_time": 210860.0,
      "text": "because, actually, in 1985,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 210110.0,
      "end_time": 211395.0,
      "text": "I graduated."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 211816.0,
      "end_time": 214604.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 216231.0,
      "end_time": 221478.0,
      "text": "You are looking at the three happiest people on the planet that day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 221502.0,
      "end_time": 223386.0,
      "text": "because I am leaving."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 223410.0,
      "end_time": 224948.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 225580.0,
      "end_time": 227786.0,
      "text": "However, the change did happen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 227810.0,
      "end_time": 231389.0,
      "text": "and today, there are 185 black students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 231413.0,
      "end_time": 235315.0,
      "text": "there are 16 black or multiracial professors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 235339.0,
      "end_time": 236960.0,
      "text": "there are four black deans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 236984.0,
      "end_time": 241484.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s an entire degree-granting Africana Studies Department."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 241508.0,
      "end_time": 244159.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 247513.0,
      "end_time": 249973.0,
      "text": "Project &#39;87 changed Davidson."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 249997.0,
      "end_time": 252974.0,
      "text": "But it also changed me, because what it taught me"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 252998.0,
      "end_time": 255757.0,
      "text": "was there&#39;s a lot of power in single-mindedness."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 256896.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259302.00000000003,
      "text": "Well, today, I&#39;m an executive speechwriter"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 259326.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261660.00000000003,
      "text": "for one of the biggest companies in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 262390.0,
      "end_time": 267152.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a profession that is 92 percent white and predominantly male,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 267177.0,
      "end_time": 269607.0,
      "text": "which makes me a little bit of a unicorn."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 270369.0,
      "end_time": 272200.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;m a single-minded unicorn."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 272260.0,
      "end_time": 273875.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 273899.0,
      "end_time": 277695.0,
      "text": "So the thing about speech writing is, it&#39;s very personal."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 277719.0,
      "end_time": 280355.0,
      "text": "So I spend a lot of time in deep conversation"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 280379.0,
      "end_time": 283549.0,
      "text": "with the CEO and senior executives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 283573.0,
      "end_time": 287909.0,
      "text": "and a lot of times those conversations turn to diversity and inclusion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 287933.0,
      "end_time": 290530.0,
      "text": "which, of course, I&#39;m always happy to talk about."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 291380.0,
      "end_time": 293691.0,
      "text": "But after quite a few of these conversations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 293715.0,
      "end_time": 295205.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve come to a conclusion:"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 295824.0,
      "end_time": 299980.0,
      "text": "I believe that business is in a position to do something"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 299122.0,
      "end_time": 301405.0,
      "text": "that no other entity can do."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 302286.0,
      "end_time": 305325.0,
      "text": "Business can dismantle racism."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 306344.0,
      "end_time": 307798.0,
      "text": "Now, colleges can&#39;t do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 307822.0,
      "end_time": 310353.0,
      "text": "There aren&#39;t but 5,000 of them in the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 310377.0,
      "end_time": 312563.0,
      "text": "and only 20 million students enrolled."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 312587.0,
      "end_time": 314700.0,
      "text": "Church can&#39;t do it, either --"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 314310.0,
      "end_time": 316798.0,
      "text": "only 35 percent of us go on a regular basis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 316822.0,
      "end_time": 318185.0,
      "text": "and when we do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 318209.0,
      "end_time": 322385.0,
      "text": "eleven o&#39;clock Sunday morning is \"the most segregated hour\" in America."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 323232.0,
      "end_time": 324632.0,
      "text": "But business?"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 324656.0,
      "end_time": 331800.0,
      "text": "There are a 162 million people in the US workforce alone --"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 331320.0,
      "end_time": 332570.0,
      "text": "people of all races,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 332595.0,
      "end_time": 337870.0,
      "text": "united in the spirit of wanting a paycheck and having to show up to get it."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 337111.0,
      "end_time": 338662.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 339458.0,
      "end_time": 343467.0,
      "text": "Now, I&#39;m aware that diversity is bigger than race,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 343491.0,
      "end_time": 345614.0,
      "text": "and racism is bigger than America."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 345638.0,
      "end_time": 349424.0,
      "text": "But racial discrimination is the most prominent form,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 349448.0,
      "end_time": 351941.0,
      "text": "and Lord knows America is the absolute best at it."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 352524.0,
      "end_time": 355956.0,
      "text": "So what if, though, what if"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 356703.0,
      "end_time": 361143.0,
      "text": "we worked in diverse and inclusive environments"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 361167.0,
      "end_time": 363297.0,
      "text": "that we had something to do something with?"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 363800.0,
      "end_time": 367517.0,
      "text": "And since we spend one-third of our lives at work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 367541.0,
      "end_time": 371248.0,
      "text": "what if we did that with people who didn&#39;t look like us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 371272.0,
      "end_time": 374936.0,
      "text": "I think the world would be a totally different place outside of work."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 375624.0,
      "end_time": 380300.0,
      "text": "That can happen if business gets single-minded about racism."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 381316.0,
      "end_time": 383789.0,
      "text": "But the question is: How is that supposed to happen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 383813.0,
      "end_time": 387594.0,
      "text": "Well, I think there are three things that business can borrow from Project &#39;87:"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 387618.0,
      "end_time": 389840.0,
      "text": "real problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 389108.0,
      "end_time": 390301.0,
      "text": "real numbers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 390325.0,
      "end_time": 391647.0,
      "text": "real consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 393235.0,
      "end_time": 394810.0,
      "text": "Like it or not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 395401.0,
      "end_time": 398870.0,
      "text": "diversity is not really a problem for business -- yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 398894.0,
      "end_time": 402354.0,
      "text": "I mean, it&#39;s a nice thing to have, it&#39;s the right thing to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 402378.0,
      "end_time": 405540.0,
      "text": "but for decades, we&#39;ve been trying to make the case"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 405780.0,
      "end_time": 409333.0,
      "text": "that diversity fuels innovation and customer insight."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 409973.0,
      "end_time": 412278.0,
      "text": "I mean, at this point, it&#39;s kind of a no-brainer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 412302.0,
      "end_time": 414791.0,
      "text": "a little bit like hearing a smoke alarm going off"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 414815.0,
      "end_time": 416899.0,
      "text": "and standing with your hand on the hot door,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 416923.0,
      "end_time": 420206.0,
      "text": "waiting for some data to tell you that your house is on fire."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 420230.0,
      "end_time": 422239.0,
      "text": "Because the data is already there."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 422904.0,
      "end_time": 427692.0,
      "text": "Ethnically diverse companies perform 33 percent better than the norm."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 428632.0,
      "end_time": 434389.0,
      "text": "Forbes&#39;s best workplaces for diversity enjoy 24 percent higher revenue growth."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 435269.0,
      "end_time": 438938.0,
      "text": "And yet, here we are in 2018,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 438962.0,
      "end_time": 443747.0,
      "text": "and there are only three black CEOs in the Fortune 500."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 443771.0,
      "end_time": 446133.0,
      "text": "And if your name is Molly or Connor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 446157.0,
      "end_time": 450409.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve got a 14 percent better chance of getting a callback on your resume"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 450433.0,
      "end_time": 452673.0,
      "text": "than if your name is Shanice or DeShawn."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 453399.0,
      "end_time": 458150.0,
      "text": "And all of this, despite the fact that by 2045,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 458174.0,
      "end_time": 463313.0,
      "text": "America is projected to be a minority-majority country."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 464207.0,
      "end_time": 465448.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s the thing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 465472.0,
      "end_time": 468890.0,
      "text": "the business case for diversity, as it stands today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 468914.0,
      "end_time": 470917.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t really speak to any problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 471472.0,
      "end_time": 474229.0,
      "text": "And the only way business is going to get single-minded"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 474253.0,
      "end_time": 476166.0,
      "text": "about racial diversity"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 476190.0,
      "end_time": 480416.0,
      "text": "is if it has a problem that is urgent and relative to somebody"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 480440.0,
      "end_time": 481999.0,
      "text": "other than people of color."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 482928.0,
      "end_time": 484140.0,
      "text": "I got one:"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 484164.0,
      "end_time": 486542.0,
      "text": "How about employees and customers?"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 487100.0,
      "end_time": 489297.0,
      "text": "Because no matter what business you&#39;re in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 489321.0,
      "end_time": 491300.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re going to need those, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 491540.0,
      "end_time": 494294.0,
      "text": "Well, let&#39;s talk about some real numbers."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 494319.0,
      "end_time": 498611.0,
      "text": "If you have employees and customers, wouldn&#39;t it make sense"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 498635.0,
      "end_time": 503320.0,
      "text": "if they looked a little bit like the people that work for you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 503345.0,
      "end_time": 508417.0,
      "text": "So if that&#39;s the case, maybe your employee base should be 13 percent Black"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 508441.0,
      "end_time": 509991.0,
      "text": "and 18 percent Hispanic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 510160.0,
      "end_time": 512389.0,
      "text": "because that&#39;s what the population looks like."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 512413.0,
      "end_time": 515491.0,
      "text": "Maybe that&#39;s what your customer base looks like."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 516169.99999999994,
      "end_time": 517378.99999999994,
      "text": "But let&#39;s be clear:"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 517403.0,
      "end_time": 520738.0,
      "text": "diversity and inclusion are not the same things."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 521421.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523547.00000000006,
      "text": "Diversity is a numbers game."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 523937.0,
      "end_time": 526890.0,
      "text": "Inclusion is about impact."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 526652.0,
      "end_time": 528886.0,
      "text": "Companies can mandate diversity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 528910.0,
      "end_time": 531218.0,
      "text": "but they have to cultivate inclusion."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 531964.0,
      "end_time": 534516.0,
      "text": "And if inclusion is what you&#39;re after,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 534540.0,
      "end_time": 537267.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve got to calculate some slightly different numbers."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 537292.0,
      "end_time": 539687.0,
      "text": "How about 30 percent?"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 540361.0,
      "end_time": 542827.0,
      "text": "Because that&#39;s the point that research shows"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 542851.0,
      "end_time": 547395.0,
      "text": "at which the voices of minorities actually begin to be heard."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 548379.0,
      "end_time": 550133.0,
      "text": "If you want a real problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 550157.0,
      "end_time": 552232.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re going to need real numbers to fix it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 552256.0,
      "end_time": 554415.0,
      "text": "and if you&#39;re not willing to set real numbers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 554439.0,
      "end_time": 557911.0,
      "text": "then maybe you&#39;re not real serious about diversity and inclusion."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 557935.0,
      "end_time": 559710.0,
      "text": "That brings me to my third point:"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 560779.0,
      "end_time": 562506.0,
      "text": "real consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 563143.0,
      "end_time": 564314.0,
      "text": "Think about this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 564338.0,
      "end_time": 568395.0,
      "text": "when salespeople forget what they&#39;re doing and don&#39;t come up with their numbers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 568419.0,
      "end_time": 569579.0,
      "text": "what do we do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 569604.0,
      "end_time": 572510.0,
      "text": "We give them a little time, maybe we give them some training."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 572534.0,
      "end_time": 574985.0,
      "text": "But then if they don&#39;t hit those numbers eventually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 575900.0,
      "end_time": 576474.0,
      "text": "we fire them."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 576498.0,
      "end_time": 579696.0,
      "text": "However, when you start talking about diversity and inclusion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 579720.0,
      "end_time": 581729.0,
      "text": "we use terms like \"accountability.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 582163.0,
      "end_time": 586497.0,
      "text": "And maybe we scold, and maybe we hold back an incentive or two."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 586521.0,
      "end_time": 588473.0,
      "text": "But you know what the best incentive is?"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 588497.0,
      "end_time": 589670.0,
      "text": "A job."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 589694.0,
      "end_time": 591769.0,
      "text": "And you know what the best disincentive is?"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 591793.0,
      "end_time": 593340.0,
      "text": "Losing it."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 593580.0,
      "end_time": 596793.0,
      "text": "So if companies really want accountability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 596817.0,
      "end_time": 598922.0,
      "text": "they should assume that that is a given."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 598946.0,
      "end_time": 603180.0,
      "text": "Consequences are what happen when you don&#39;t do what you&#39;re accountable for."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 604426.0,
      "end_time": 606414.0,
      "text": "Imagine this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 606438.0,
      "end_time": 613189.0,
      "text": "imagine a place where people of all colors and all races"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 613213.0,
      "end_time": 617905.0,
      "text": "are on and climbing every rung of the corporate ladder;"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 617929.0,
      "end_time": 622270.0,
      "text": "where those people feel safe -- indeed, expected --"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 622294.0,
      "end_time": 626771.0,
      "text": "to bring their unassimilated, authentic selves to work every day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 626796.0,
      "end_time": 631897.0,
      "text": "because the difference that they bring is both recognized and respected."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 632511.0,
      "end_time": 638213.0,
      "text": "And imagine a place where the lessons we learn about diversity at work"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 638237.0,
      "end_time": 643666.0,
      "text": "actually transform the things we do, think and say outside of work."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 644288.0,
      "end_time": 647176.0,
      "text": "That is what happens if we all work together"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 647200.0,
      "end_time": 648738.0,
      "text": "to fix what&#39;s broken."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 648762.0,
      "end_time": 652396.0,
      "text": "That is what happens if we stop praying for change to happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 652420.0,
      "end_time": 654997.0,
      "text": "and actually start moving our feet to making it."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 655551.0,
      "end_time": 658470.0,
      "text": "That is the power of single-mindedness."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 658710.0,
      "end_time": 659231.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 659255.0,
      "end_time": 662114.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}